content: अन्यतम {%<ab>a.</ab>%} [अन्य-डतम] (declined like a noun and not a pronoun) One of many, any one out of a large number (with <ab>gen.</ab> or in <ab>comp.</ab>); जपन्वान्यतमं वेदं <ls>Ms. 11. 76</ls>; <ls n="Ms.">6. 32</ls>, <ls n="Ms.">4. 13</ls>; <ls>Y. 2. 22</ls>, <ls n="Y.">3. 253</ls>; ( अन्यतरान्यतमशब्दौ अव्युत्पन्नौ प्रातिपदिके इति कैयटः).
